Package: uspto
Title: USPTO (US Patent and Trademark Office) Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the USPTO Dataset API (DS-API). Provides
    search and access to patent office actions, prior art citations, claim
    rejections, and enriched citation metadata via the Solr-based REST API at
    developer.uspto.gov.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    dplyr,
    tibble
